bill.summary: 4/2/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1997, the duty on a-isopropyl-a ((N-methyl-N-homoveratryl)-g-aminopropyl)-3, 4-dimethoxy-phenylacetonitril-hydrochloride.
